<h2><a name='sect0' href='#toc0'>Name</a></h2>
<p>
C]MPI_Comm_call_errhandlerR] - Passes the supplied error code to
the error handler assigned to a communicator
<h2><a name='sect1' href='#toc1'>Syntax</a></h2>

